  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Regadenoson is approved in the US under the brand name Lexiscan for myocardial perfusion
      imaging. This study will test whether regadenoson is an appropriate stress agent for stress
      echocardiography.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
